Instead of comparing the iterator‚Äôs elements directly, this function compares the keys of the elements, as determined by `f`. Apart from that, it‚Äôs equivalent to [`is_sorted`](about:blank/trait.Iterator.html#method.is_sorted "method std::iter::Iterator::is_sorted"); see its documentation for more information.

